  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nAnvil\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nWhen using --silent, I know it says in docs it only silents the startup, but it would be nice to silence the JSON-RPC method names being called to avoid spamming the logs if you do not care for it.\r\n\r\nThe use case is if you are trying to run a local node in a `child_process`, you have to override the max buffer to infinity for it not to bail out after it's been running for x time over just being able to do --silent and make it run in the background without any noise.\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_",
